<section class="py-32 bg-surface-container">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-label-md text-secondary mb-4 block">Our Expertise</span>
      <h2 class="text-display-md text-primary">We can help you engage with...</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-10 shadow-lg border-t-4 border-secondary hover:transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary mb-6 block">handshake</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Medical Providers & Referral Partners</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Increase visibility with providers in the community and expand your referrals sources. Fuel growth through strategic partners to ensure a foundation of sustainable and predictable growth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-10 shadow-lg border-t-4 border-secondary hover:transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary mb-6 block">groups</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Community Outreach and Engagement</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Let’s strategize on how to build on the great work already being done locally and develop new initiatives to meet the challenges.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-10 shadow-lg border-t-4 border-secondary hover:transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary mb-6 block">campaign</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Media Relations, PR and Events</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Leverage relationships with the media to partner for events and attract more people and increase visibility.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-10 shadow-lg border-t-4 border-secondary hover:transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary mb-6 block">devices</span>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Online Tools</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">Use online tools and social media to communicate with a wide audience and provide education and localize your content so people know where to find your services.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>